{"tid":1269651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IFC 唔好再喺現場嚟行為藝術去掉念死者","createTime":"2019-06-30T15:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T05:22:15.000Z","uid":260988,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"498b8b5694ffc8e14ee0d91854b6497d16266739","tid":1269651,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"希望大家用慣常嘅鮮花、默哀、留字句等等去悼念死者，因為咁係最易令常人理解，最易傳播心中理念<br />\n<br />\n希望唔好再喺現場用行為藝術悼念死者，如果又好似 PP 咁一堆人擺個鍊成陣，件事就真好膠"},{"pid":"b8fd68cd3429041a116befe3b8f6ec56d0917655","tid":1269651,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab7eea03968dee267e31c5445bcfc35ae1aaeee5","tid":1269651,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b75b2c1dfe727cad76319dbc4c14dff7ab98d66","tid":1269651,"uid":42767,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:46:11.000Z","msg":"放心, IFC啲保安惡過狗, 無PP果啲咁有人性"},{"pid":"d15d3795893218a2df479f1f72cab314fcdfd320","tid":1269651,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4465e0ab1795bf259f12e627ba1bf77e9f25b03c","tid":1269651,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:47:40.000Z","msg":"中共已經建國70年，按照現代極權法西斯統治嘅歷史規律，中共倒台只係時間嘅問題，大家一定要保住條命，親眼見證歷史一刻，屬於我地香港人勝利嘅一日<br />\n<br />\n【長文，但希望大家可以睇晒】香港人一定會贏，所以真係唔使死、唔好死。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267076\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267076</a>"},{"pid":"4a5d587eb159bea3df97f9062aaa171cc1070057","tid":1269651,"uid":260988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"092a40e4af939f0aef8c4abc7ac9a7c7f944482c","tid":1269651,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b75b2c1dfe727cad76319dbc4c14dff7ab98d66","tid":1269651,"uid":42767,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime